==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unusual
<hw>Un*u"su*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not usual;
uncommon; rare; <as>as, an <ex>unusual</ex> season; a person of
<ex>unusual</ex> grace or erudition.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*u"su*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*u"su*al*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unusuality</ent>⟦br⟧
